title: Wind EPACT-STEP  - Mihir Desai (University of Texas, San Antonio)

info.x_cadence_note: Counts based on variable 'Epoch' in https://cdaweb.gsfc.nasa.gov/sp_phys/data/wind/epact/step/differential-ion-flux-1hr/wi_epact_step-differential-ion-flux-1hr_19941121_v01.cdf. The most common cadence, 3612305 [ms] = PT1H12.305S, occurred for 16.2743% of the 159 timesteps.
info.contact: Mihir Desai @ University of Texas, San Antonio
